#### Reference Issues/PRs

Fixes #778

#### What does this implement/fix? Explain your changes.
<!--
A clear and concise description of what you have implemented.
-->
Adds `_guerrero` function for lambda estimation to `BoxCoxTransformer`.
This method is tested in `test_boxcox.py` in `test_lambda_bounds` and in `test_guerrero_against_r_implementation`.

-->
No.
